## Lab-Grown: The Tax-Free Path to 2ct

Lab-grown diamonds eliminate The Size Jump Tax because their supply is not constrained by rough crystal rarity. A lab can produce 2ct D-VVS1 rough routinely. Natural cannot.

![lab-grown 2 carat round diamond IGI certified D-VVS1 compared to natural 1 carat GIA certified G-VS2 price comparison on white editorial background](/images/round-diamond-1-carat-vs-2-carat-2.avif)

**Lab progression — IGI Excellent, all D-VVS1 unless noted:**

| Stone | Carat | Clarity | Price | Per-Carat | vs Natural Equiv. |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| [IGI 1.5ct D-VVS1 Lab](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28134308?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 1.5ct | D-VVS1 | $1,950 | $1,300 | Natural 1.5ct ≈ $7,000+ |
| [IGI 2ct D-VVS1 Lab](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29116588?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 2ct | D-VVS1 | $2,810 | $1,405 | Natural 2ct G-VS2: $16,490 |
| [IGI 2ct D-FL Lab](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29149727?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 2ct | D-FL | $5,190 | $2,595 | Natural 2ct D-FL: $54,840 |
| [GIA 3ct D-VVS1 Lab](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/29116162?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 3ct | D-VVS1 | $7,340 | $2,447 | Natural 3ct G-VS2: $48,780 |
| [IGI 4ct D-VVS1 Lab](https://www.bluenile.com/diamond-details/28884761?a_aid=69d7c31a91b8d&a_cid=55e51e63&chan=blog-informational) | 4ct | D-VVS1 | $9,680 | $2,420 | Natural 4ct G-VS1: $58,110 |

The lab 2ct D-VVS1 at $2,810 is $420 cheaper than the natural 1ct G-VS2 at $3,230. It is also:
- 60% larger face-up area (8.1mm vs 6.4mm)
- D color vs G color — two grades better
- VVS1 clarity vs VS2 clarity — three grades better
- Graded by IGI with Excellent cut vs GIA Excellent

For a buyer prioritizing visible size and certified quality within any budget under $5,000, the lab 2ct D-VVS1 at $2,810 is the logical choice.

